document.full_text: as britney spears prepares to launch her seventh studio album "femme fatale" on tuesday, the pop star faces keen competition from lady gaga, katie perry and rihanna, who reign atop billboard's hot 100 singles ranking.
document.title: britney is back, but can she compete with gaga?
